      • getNoteID

        int getNoteID()
        Retrieves the note ID for the entry. This may be the ID of the document for a document row, or a special ID for a category row.
        Returns:
        the note ID value for the entry

      • getUNID

        String getUNID()
        Retrieves the UNID associated with the entry, if it is a document.
        Returns:
        the UNID of the entry's document, or an all-zero string if is not a document

      • isCategory

        boolean isCategory()
        Determines whether the collection entry represents a category, as opposed to a document or total row.
        Returns:

      • isDocument

        Determines whether the collection entry represents a document, as opposed to a category or total row.
        Returns:
        true if the entry represents a document; false otherwise
